<div id="review_2533167819" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2533167819" />
    <a title="Aisha Manus" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/10969599-aisha-manus"><img alt="Aisha Manus" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1603584344p2/10969599.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2533167819?book_show_action=true">Sep 27, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Aisha Manus" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Aisha Manus" href="/user/show/10969599-aisha-manus">Aisha Manus</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2533167819" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4567366870782024451">3.5 stars. Much more than I expected. Wasn’t sure I liked it in the beginning but it picked up as it went on. You can tell that she writes poetry by the way she wrote this. Interesting and would recommend to certain people. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


