<div id="review_2254180560" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2254180560" />
    <a title="Maya Mitchell" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/76370753-maya-mitchell"><img alt="Maya Mitchell" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1518161427p2/76370753.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2254180560?book_show_action=true">Feb 08, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Maya Mitchell" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Maya Mitchell" href="/user/show/76370753-maya-mitchell">Maya Mitchell</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2254180560" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer863212564465907743">A powerful &amp; beautifully descriptive read. <br/><br/>I must admit, it took me awhile to get into the flow of the story &amp; become emotionally connected to the story. However, the poetic undertones in each chapter &amp; illustrative narrative got me hooked once I committed to reading the book in its entirety. At first, I thought the story to be one solely about a couple in love while facing grave adversity. But then I started to detect various truths within the text; the most prominent being self love &amp; healing!</span>
  <span id="freeText863212564465907743" style="display:none">A powerful &amp; beautifully descriptive read. <br /><br />I must admit, it took me awhile to get into the flow of the story &amp; become emotionally connected to the story. However, the poetic undertones in each chapter &amp; illustrative narrative got me hooked once I committed to reading the book in its entirety. At first, I thought the story to be one solely about a couple in love while facing grave adversity. But then I started to detect various truths within the text; the most prominent being self love &amp; healing! What a powerful message portrayed through such incredible words.<br /><br />Loved it &amp; would highly recommend. </span>
  <a data-text-id="863212564465907743" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

