        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2090298924" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5474989135285647419">Bandele offers an emotional glimpse into the lives of two people romantically involved within the constraints of prison walls, both physically and emotionally present. Her writing glides readers through the memoir, touching feelings and navigating challenges faced in such an unusual yet all too common set of circumstances. She left this reader feeling familiar with the couple, hoping they will prevail. I&apos;m looking forward to reading other books she&apos;s written.</span>
  <span id="freeText5474989135285647419" style="display:none">Bandele offers an emotional glimpse into the lives of two people romantically involved within the constraints of prison walls, both physically and emotionally present. Her writing glides readers through the memoir, touching feelings and navigating challenges faced in such an unusual yet all too common set of circumstances. She left this reader feeling familiar with the couple, hoping they will prevail. I'm looking forward to reading other books she's written.</span>
